properties.occurrenceRemarks: Jaguar killing a caiman! This is Patricia, an alpha female with two nearly grown cubs to feed, and that caiman was as big as she was. She stalked it along the hyacinths and dispatched it fairly quickly with a bite to the head, then dragged it deeper into the water plants so we could not see her and her cubs feed. These are bad photos (I have somewhat better video) but hopefully friends at different angles have better ones. What an amazing thing to see.
